{With your 12 point hand you need to force to game. It would also be nice to find out if partner has a 4-card \H suit. Since you have East's \S suit stopped, you first bid a lebensohl 2NT.

Partner says 3\C.  

NOW you cue-bid 3\S. This is Stayman, but with a \S stopper, (SLOW SHOWS). Partner says 3NT and you pass.

}

